21. Ra2 Rxc4 $15 {0-1 (57) Peralta,F (2580)-Aronian,L (2767) Caleta ENG 2019})
({It is probably not the right time and place for} 14. Bc2 Ne7 (14... Na5 $5
15. Qd3 Qc7 $15 {would also work.}) 15. Qd3 Qd5 16. Bg5 Ng6 {White's simple
threat has been prevented and he is left with a backward pawn on c3.} 17. Rac1
Qa5 18. Bxf6 gxf6 $15 {0-1 (42) Mijovic,S (2404)-Berkes,F (2658) Arad 2014}) {
Here, Black's setup can be improved with:} 14... h6 $5 $146 15. Bh4 (15. Bd2
