Black gets good counterplay with} Ne7 15. Ne5 Nf5 $132) 13... Nbd7 14. Bd2 Nd5
15. Rad1 Bf4 {and upcoming exchanges are in Black's favor.} 16. Nxd5 Bxd2 17.
