12. Be2 {[#]} Re6 $1 13. O-O Rg6 $36) 7... c5 8. Bg5 (8. Nf3 {-6.Nf3}) 8... h6
9. Bxf6 Qxf6 10. e3 O-O 11. Nf3 Nc6 12. Be2 Be6 13. O-O Rac8 $11 {Again, this
