Qxa7 $2 Qxd4+ 21. Kc2 Qd2+ {with a mating attack.}) 20... Qe3 21. Rc2 Nf2+ 22.
Ke1 Nd3+ 23. Kd1 Nf2+ $11 {½-½ (27) Andriasian,Z (2598)-Grigoryan,A (2599)
Yerevan 2013} *

