18. Rc1 Ke7 19. Nd4 Rhc8 $11 {0-1 (43) Borzov,D (2133)-Ashwin,J (2472) Varna
2013}) (12. Nge2 {can be met the same way as in 11.Nge2 line:} Bf5 13. Nd4 {
