$5 $146 {is an interesting new idea, with the following point:} 18. Kf2 $6 d4
19. exd4 O-O $1 20. Be5 Rfe8 $36) ({The most interesting continuation is:} 16.
h4 Nxc5 17. Rd1 g4 18. Rd4 Qa6 {[#] with double-edged play:} 19. h5 (19. Rxg4
