position.}) (6. Nf3 {directly transposes into Chapter 15:4.Nf3 b6 Nimzo-Indian
after} h6 7. Bh4 g5 8. Bg3 Ne4 {etc.}) 6... O-O 7. Nf3 d6 {[#] Black completes
his development, but keeps the plan with ...h6, g5 and Ne4 (that will be in
