Nf4 Re8 13. Bxf6 (13. Bxc4 Nxe4 $1 $17) (13. O-O-O g5 $17) 13... Qxf6 14. Bxc4
Bxe4 $1 {Black's strategy has been a success. However, White keeps some
compensation after:} 15. O-O $44 Bb7 16. Nfd5 Bxd5 17. Qxd5 $44) ({Developing
continuation} 7. Nh3 {also deserves attention. Now Black clears up the center
