-Sadilek,P (2248)/Vienna 2016/CBM 174 Extra (34)}) 8... Nxd5 $5 {8...exd5
would also do the job, but this is cooler.} 9. Bxd5 (9. exd5 $4 Qh4+ 10. Nf2
