14... Qf6 15. Rc1 Bb6 $40 {[#] The bishops completely dominate!} 16. Rd1 Nd4
17. Bf4 Rac8 18. Qg5 Qe6 19. Rd2 Qb3 $19 {0-1 Nakar,E (2471)-Sevian,S (2590)/
