[#] White already faces some difficulties.} 15. a3 ({In case of} 15. Kg1 {
Black obtains an advantage thanks to some high-level tactics:} Bc4 16. Qd2 d5
$1 17. exd5 Bxa2 $1 18. Rxa2 Nc4 19. Qd3 Rxe3 $1 20. Qxc4 Bxc3 $17) 15... Bc4
$17 {0-1 (34) Hammer,J (2647)-Hess,R (2572) Moscow 2011}) ({It makes sense to
