17. Rad1 O-O-O $17 {0-1 (39) Moskalenko,V (2460)-Novikov,I (2460) Lvov 1985}) (
{Releasing central tension prematurely with} 8. d5 {is not prudent, as we have
seen in Karpov's game above. Two games below should help confirm this
