against White's central expansion plan is:} 9... Re8 10. Nf4 Bd6 11. f3 {
and now} Bc7 $1 12. b4 ({If} 12. e4 {then} dxe4 13. fxe4 Bb6 14. Nfe2 Bg4 $132
