15. Na4 Nbd7 16. Bb2 Bc7 17. Rc1 a5 $1 $15 {1/2-1/2 (60) Gajewski,G (2577)
-Lenic,L (2569) Dresden 2008}) 10. Nf4 Nc7 11. f3 c5 (11... Ne6 $5 12. Nxe6
